name: The Humble Celestial
description: The sun. It shines throughout the day. Setting by the horizon for the night skies to take over. Have you ever sat by yourself sipping some tea and witnessing this magical moment the nature has to offer? A humble celestial the sun is, radiating warmth and life force. Always giving never expecting. I thank you Sun for your ever giving essence. Looking at this piece to remind. To appreciate this consciousness of the divine.
